7. When prompted, choose to save the file, and save it into the &quot;C:\  Drivers\Audio&quot; directory you just created.  DO NOT RUN the file yet.<br>
8. Copy and paste this address into your browser: <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://download.microsoft.com/download/win98/Install/8.1/W98Me/EN-US/DX81eng.exe">download.microsoft.com/download/win98/Install/8.1/W98Me/EN-US/DX81eng.exe</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.  This is the DirectX 8.1 drivers for Win98/ME.<br>
9. When prompted, choose to save the file, and save it into the &quot;C:\  Drivers\DirectX&quot; directory you just created.  DO NOT RUN the file yet.<br>
